Please share all installed IMG-Files and the PRODUCT.TDB located in the Family_535 directory,
i.e. c:\Programme\Garmin\Mapsource\FAMILY_535 (Not the files located on disk). Then it's possible
to integrate the unlocked files in Mapsource.

Editing the Registry in this way should work.

REGEDIT4

[HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SOFTWARE\Garmin\MapSource\Families\FAMILY_535\1]
"Bmap"="C:\Programme\Garmin\FAMILY_535\basemap.img"
"Tdb"="C:\Programme\Garmin\FAMILY_535\product.tdb"
"Loc"="C:\Programme\Garmin\FAMILY_535"
